        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-01-07 23:02:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f0a01df4-591a-11e2-95fa-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
