        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-01-08 04:39:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI was worrying about the barrier problem, but seems set_current_state() & wakeup() do implied barrier, so I agreed this fix isn't necessary.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
