      "date": "2013-01-17 19:09:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/6552f04c-60d5-11e2-a224-52540035b04c).  Ran 18 tests.  3 tests failed: replay-ost-single, recovery-small, replay-single.",
